subject: Re: Welcome To
body:
Hello,

Thank you for reaching out to me from Charles Schwab Bank. I appreciate the information you have provided about the services your bank offers. It sounds interesting.

I have a few questions regarding the ATM Visa card you mentioned. Could you please clarify how this card works? How can I use it to withdraw money and make purchases online? Also, what are the fees associated with using this card?

Additionally, I would like to know more about the Worldwide Courier Company that will be delivering the ATM card. Can you provide more details about their services and how they ensure safe delivery?

Thank you for your assistance. I look forward to hearing back from you soon.

Best wishes,
Phil
